An **Online Ticket Reservation 
System** is a digital platform that
allows users to book and purchase t
ickets for events, transportation,
movies, or other services via the i
nternet. It provides a convenient w
ay to check availability, select
seats, make secure payments,
and receive e-tickets instantly
. The system benefits both customer
s and businesses by streamlining the
booking process, reducing manual work
, and enabling real-time updates
. Features often include user 
accounts, payment gateways,
booking confirmations, and 
cancellation options. Examples include platforms like BookMyShow, Ticketmaster, and airline booking websites.
